command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
M18Z0 ; disable Z motor, spring will Zero the seesaw; G0 will turn back on
G4 P500 ; give enough time for z to get to neutral
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
; should be never called, since specifying nozzle PUMP_ON_COMMAND
; should be never called, since specifying nozzle PUMP_OFF_COMMAND
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
; not used by automation, just Actuator buttons
;dummy to prevent default from being called
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
;dummy to prevent default from being called
;dummy to prevent default from being called
; No pumps but blow solonoid needs to be off
M{True:50}{False:51} ; Send "M50 to drop pin and M51 to raise"
G92 Z0A0 ; do not want to be in relative mode, for XY, so just reset peel steppers
G0 {Z:X%.4f} {A:Y%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Z is X axis, A is Y axis
G0 A{Distance:%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.2f} ; A is left extruder
